def main():
    n = int(input())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    a.sort()
    a.reverse()
    alice = 0
    bob = 0
    for i in range(n):
        if i % 2 == 0:
            alice += a[i]
        else:
            bob += a[i]
    print(alice - bob)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
